&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note:&lt;/strong&gt; Obtain your access token from Splunk Observability Cloud: &lt;strong&gt;Settings → Access Tokens&lt;/strong&gt; (Ingest token with APM permissions).. You will need to paste them into configs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
 &lt;div class="code-block__header"&gt;
 &lt;span class="code-block__file"&gt;&lt;span class="code-block__lang"&gt;bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
