 &lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;You should see a JSON response like:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>3. Check Splunk</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/instrumentation/19-context-propagation/3-deploy-splunk-otel-collector/3-check-splunk/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/instrumentation/19-context-propagation/3-deploy-splunk-otel-collector/3-check-splunk/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="confirm-infrastructure-metrics-in-splunk"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;Confirm Infrastructure Metrics in Splunk&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#confirm-infrastructure-metrics-in-splunk" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="callout callout--success"&gt;&lt;span class="callout__icon" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p class="callout__title"&gt;Note&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="callout__body"&gt;Allow &lt;strong&gt;2–5 minutes&lt;/strong&gt; after deploy for infrastructure metrics to appear..&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open &lt;strong&gt;Infrastructure → Kubernetes&lt;/strong&gt; (or &lt;strong&gt;Infrastructure Monitoring&lt;/strong&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Filter by cluster &lt;strong&gt;&lt;code&gt;trace-workshop&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; (&lt;code&gt;k8s.cluster.name&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confirm node CPU/memory and pod metrics (for example &lt;code&gt;k8s.node.*&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;k8s.pod.*&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;system.cpu.*&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="callout callout--note"&gt;&lt;span class="callout__icon" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p class="callout__title"&gt;Note&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="callout__body"&gt;All infrastructure metrics are tagged with &lt;code&gt;k8s.cluster.name=trace-workshop-&amp;lt;your-Initials&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; (from &lt;code&gt;K8S_CLUSTER_NAME&lt;/code&gt; in &lt;code&gt;workshop-config&lt;/code&gt; ConfigMap).&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If infrastructure metrics are missing:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>